OL,6,FThe family of Katie Simpson have told
OL,7,FUTV they feel justice was 'robbed'
OL,8,Ffrom them after the man accused of
OL,9,Fmurdering the talented showjumper died
OL,10,Fsuddenly 24 hours after the trial
OL,11,Fstarted.
