OL,6,FThe 21-year-old said: "Katie was a
OL,7,Frole model. She taught me to not be
OL,8,Fscared of anything. She was like the
OL,9,Fbig sister I never had. She was at the
OL,10,Fcentre of my childhood. We miss her
OL,11,Feveryday and wish she was still here."
OL,13,FColleen added: "Katie was so fun-
OL,14,Floving and really enjoyed going out.
OL,15,FWhen she was younger she was always
OL,16,Fjust full of life, she got you in a
OL,17,Fgood mood.
OL,19,F"She was just great to be around, like
OL,20,Fa role model as well."
